---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout 
  title="What to Expect | Your First Visit to BareCanvas"
  description="Everything you need to know about your waxing appointment at BareCanvas. Step-by-step process, preparation tips, and comfort measures to ease first-time anxiety."
>
  <section class="hero-section expect-hero">
    <div class="hero-background-logo"></div>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="hero-content animate-on-scroll fade-up">
        <div class="gold-accent-line"></div>
        <h1>What to Expect</h1>
        <div class="gold-highlight"></div>
        <p class="hero-subtitle">Your complete guide to a comfortable, professional waxing experience</p>
        <p class="hero-description">
          First time? Feeling nervous? Let us walk you through exactly what happens during your visit so you feel completely prepared and at ease.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="process-timeline">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header animate-on-scroll fade-up">
        <h2>Your Step-by-Step Experience</h2>
        <p>Every appointment follows the same careful, professional process</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="timeline">
        <div class="timeline-item animate-on-scroll fade-left">
          <div class="timeline-number">1</div>
          <div class="timeline-content">
            <h3>Warm Welcome & Consultation</h3>
            <p>When you arrive, you'll be greeted in our comfortable, clean environment. We'll start with a brief consultation to discuss your needs, preferences, and any concerns you might have.</p>
            <div class="timeline-details">
              <span class="detail-tag">5 minutes</span>
              <span class="detail-tag">No pressure</span>
              <span class="detail-tag">All questions welcome</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="timeline-item animate-on-scroll fade-right">
          <div class="timeline-number">2</div>
          <div class="timeline-content">
            <h3>Preparation & Setup</h3>
            <p>I'll explain exactly what will happen during your service and answer any last-minute questions. You'll have complete privacy to prepare, and I'll ensure the room is at a comfortable temperature.</p>
            <div class="timeline-details">
              <span class="detail-tag">Private room</span>
              <span class="detail-tag">Your comfort first</span>
              <span class="detail-tag">Professional setup</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="timeline-item animate-on-scroll fade-left">
          <div class="timeline-number">3</div>
          <div class="timeline-content">
            <h3>Professional Waxing Process</h3>
            <p>Using high-quality wax and professional techniques, I work efficiently while prioritizing your comfort. I'll communicate throughout the process and check in with you regularly.</p>
            <div class="timeline-details">
              <span class="detail-tag">Professional technique</span>
              <span class="detail-tag">Constant communication</span>
              <span class="detail-tag">Your pace</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="timeline-item animate-on-scroll fade-right">
          <div class="timeline-number">4</div>
          <div class="timeline-content">
            <h3>Soothing Aftercare</h3>
            <p>Once complete, I'll apply soothing products to minimize any redness and provide you with detailed aftercare instructions. You'll leave feeling smooth and confident.</p>
            <div class="timeline-details">
              <span class="detail-tag">Soothing products</span>
              <span class="detail-tag">Aftercare guide</span>
              <span class="detail-tag">Follow-up support</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="preparation-guide">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="guide-grid">
        <div class="guide-section animate-on-scroll fade-up">
          <div class="guide-icon">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
              <path d="M12 2L15.09 8.26L22 9.27L17 14.14L18.18 21.02L12 17.77L5.82 21.02L7 14.14L2 9.27L8.91 8.26L12 2Z" stroke="var(--warm-brown)" stroke-width="2" fill="var(--muted-gold)" opacity="0.3"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Before Your Appointment</h3>
          <ul class="checklist">
            <li>Hair should be ¼ to ½ inch long (about 2-3 weeks of growth)</li>
            <li>Gently exfoliate 24-48 hours before your appointment</li>
            <li>Avoid sun exposure and tanning for 24 hours prior</li>
            <li>Skip caffeine on the day of your appointment to reduce sensitivity</li>
            <li>Wear comfortable, loose-fitting clothing</li>
            <li>Take an over-the-counter pain reliever 30 minutes before if desired</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="guide-section animate-on-scroll fade-up">
          <div class="guide-icon">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
              <path d="M20.84 4.61A5.5 5.5 0 0 0 16.5 2.03A5.5 5.5 0 0 0 12 4.53A5.5 5.5 0 0 0 7.5 2.03A5.5 5.5 0 0 0 3.16 4.61C2.42 5.81 2.5 7.27 3.34 8.4L12 21.47L20.66 8.4C21.5 7.27 21.58 5.81 20.84 4.61Z" stroke="var(--warm-brown)" stroke-width="2" fill="var(--muted-gold)" opacity="0.3"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Comfort Measures</h3>
          <ul class="checklist">
            <li>Professional-grade wax that adheres to hair, not skin</li>
            <li>Gentle pulling technique to minimize discomfort</li>
            <li>Immediate pressure applied to soothe the area</li>
            <li>Cool, soothing products to reduce any redness</li>
            <li>Room temperature adjusted for your comfort</li>
            <li>Breaks available anytime you need them</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="guide-section animate-on-scroll fade-up">
          <div class="guide-icon">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
              <path d="M22 12H18L15 21L9 3L6 12H2" stroke="var(--warm-brown)" stroke-width="2"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3>After Your Service</h3>
          <ul class="checklist">
            <li>Avoid hot showers, baths, or saunas for 24 hours</li>
            <li>Skip the gym and intense physical activity for 24 hours</li>
            <li>Wear loose, breathable clothing</li>
            <li>Apply the recommended aftercare products as directed</li>
            <li>Gently exfoliate 2-3 days after to prevent ingrown hairs</li>
            <li>Schedule your next appointment in 4-6 weeks</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="anxiety-relief">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="relief-content animate-on-scroll fade-up">
        <h2>Feeling Nervous? You're Not Alone</h2>
        <p class="lead">It's completely normal to feel anxious about your first waxing appointment. Here's what our clients want you to know:</p>
        
        <div class="relief-grid">
          <div class="relief-card animate-on-scroll scale-in">
            <h4>"It was much less painful than I expected"</h4>
            <p>Most first-time clients are pleasantly surprised by how manageable the experience is with professional technique and quality products.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="relief-card animate-on-scroll scale-in">
            <h4>"Priscilla made me feel completely comfortable"</h4>
            <p>Professional, experienced estheticians know exactly how to put you at ease and guide you through the process with care.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="relief-card animate-on-scroll scale-in">
            <h4>"She explains everything beforehand"</h4>
            <p>No surprises. You'll know exactly what to expect at each step, and you can ask questions anytime throughout the process.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="relief-card animate-on-scroll scale-in">
            <h4>"The results last so much longer than shaving"</h4>
            <p>Once you experience the smooth, long-lasting results of professional waxing, you'll understand why clients become regulars.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="environment-showcase">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="showcase-content">
        <div class="showcase-text animate-on-scroll fade-left">
          <h2>A Clean, Professional Environment</h2>
          <p>Your comfort and safety are our top priorities. Our professional suite features:</p>
          <div class="features-list">
            <div class="feature-item">
              <div class="feature-icon">
                <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                  <path d="M9 12L11 14L15 10" stroke="var(--muted-gold)" stroke-width="2"/>
                  <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10" stroke="var(--warm-brown)" stroke-width="2"/>
                </svg>
              </div>
              <span>Hospital-grade sanitation standards</span>
            </div>
            <div class="feature-item">
              <div class="feature-icon">
                <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                  <path d="M9 12L11 14L15 10" stroke="var(--muted-gold)" stroke-width="2"/>
                  <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10" stroke="var(--warm-brown)" stroke-width="2"/>
                </svg>
              </div>
              <span>Private, comfortable treatment room</span>
            </div>
            <div class="feature-item">
              <div class="feature-icon">
                <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                  <path d="M9 12L11 14L15 10" stroke="var(--muted-gold)" stroke-width="2"/>
                  <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10" stroke="var(--warm-brown)" stroke-width="2"/>
                </svg>
              </div>
              <span>Professional-grade products and equipment</span>
            </div>
            <div class="feature-item">
              <div class="feature-icon">
                <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                  <path d="M9 12L11 14L15 10" stroke="var(--muted-gold)" stroke-width="2"/>
                  <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10" stroke="var(--warm-brown)" stroke-width="2"/>
                </svg>
              </div>
              <span>Located in a professional suite building</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="showcase-visual animate-on-scroll fade-right">
          <div class="visual-placeholder">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 500 400" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
              <rect width="500" height="400" fill="var(--light-beige)" rx="12"/>
              <rect x="50" y="50" width="400" height="300" fill="white" rx="8"/>
              <rect x="80" y="80" width="150" height="100" fill="var(--warm-cream)" rx="4"/>
              <rect x="270" y="80" width="150" height="100" fill="var(--muted-gold)" opacity="0.3" rx="4"/>
              <rect x="80" y="220" width="340" height="60" fill="var(--warm-brown)" opacity="0.2" rx="4"/>
              <circle cx="400" cy="120" r="30" fill="var(--muted-gold)" opacity="0.4"/>
              <text x="250" y="340" text-anchor="middle" fill="var(--warm-brown)" font-size="14" font-family="Inter">Professional Treatment Room</text>
            </svg>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="cta-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="cta-content animate-on-scroll fade-up">
        <h2>Ready to Book Your First Appointment?</h2>
        <p>Still have questions? Feel free to call and we'll be happy to discuss anything that's on your mind</p>
        <div class="cta-buttons">
          <a href="https://www.vagaro.com/barecanvas/services" class="btn btn-primary" target="_blank">
            Book Online Now
          </a>
          <a href="tel:832-570-9458" class="btn btn-secondary">
            Call with Questions
          </a>
        </div>
        <div class="contact-info">
          <p><strong>BareCanvas</strong> • Suite 804, 2743 Smith Ranch Rd, Pearland, TX</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .hero-section {
    padding: 8rem 0 4rem;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--warm-cream) 0%, var(--light-beige) 50%, #f0e6d6 100%);
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .hero-background-logo {
    position: absolute;
    top: 50%;
    left: 50%;
    transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
    width: 700px;
    height: 700px;
    background-image: url('/images/Bare-Canvas-TP-Logo.png');
    background-size: contain;
    background-repeat: no-repeat;
    background-position: center;
    opacity: 0.08;
    z-index: 1;
    animation: logoFloat 8s ease-in-out infinite;
  }

  @keyframes logoFloat {
    0%, 100% { 
      transform: translate(-50%, -50%) rotate(0deg) scale(1);
      opacity: 0.08;
    }
    50% { 
      transform: translate(-50%, -50%) rotate(2deg) scale(1.05);
      opacity: 0.12;
    }
  }

  .container {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 2rem;
  }

  .hero-content {
    text-align: center;
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 2;
  }

  .gold-accent-line {
    width: 80px;
    height: 4px;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--muted-gold), #d4af37, var(--muted-gold));
    border-radius: 2px;
    margin: 0 auto 1.5rem;
    box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.3);
  }

  .hero-content h1 {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: 3.5rem;
    font-weight: 400;
    color: var(--deep-brown);
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    line-height: 1.1;
    text-shadow: 0 2px 4px rgba(74, 53, 40, 0.1);
  }

  .gold-highlight {
    width: 120px;
    height: 3px;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, var(--muted-gold), #d4af37, var(--muted-gold), transparent);
    margin: 0.5rem auto 2rem;
    border-radius: 2px;
    animation: shimmer 3s ease-in-out infinite;
  }

  @keyframes shimmer {
    0%, 100% { opacity: 0.6; transform: scaleX(1); }
    50% { opacity: 1; transform: scaleX(1.1); }
  }

  .hero-subtitle {
    font-size: 1.4rem;
    color: var(--warm-brown);
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  .hero-description {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    color: var(--warm-brown);
    line-height: 1.6;
    max-width: 600px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .process-timeline {
    padding: 6rem 0;
    background: white;
  }

  .section-header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 4rem;
  }

  .section-header h2 {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    color: var(--deep-brown);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .section-header p {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    color: var(--warm-brown);
  }

  .timeline {
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    position: relative;
  }

  .timeline::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    left: 50%;
    top: 0;
    bottom: 0;
    width: 2px;
    background: var(--muted-gold);
    transform: translateX(-50%);
  }

  .timeline-item {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    margin-bottom: 4rem;
    position: relative;
  }

  .timeline-item:nth-child(even) {
    flex-direction: row-reverse;
  }

  .timeline-number {
    width: 60px;
    height: 60px;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--muted-gold), #d4af37);
    border-radius: 50%;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--deep-brown);
    box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.3);
    position: relative;
    z-index: 2;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .timeline-content {
    flex: 1;
    background: white;
    padding: 2.5rem;
    border-radius: 16px;
    box-shadow: 0 12px 40px rgba(74, 53, 40, 0.08);
    border: 1px solid rgba(196, 163, 115, 0.2);
    margin: 0 2rem;
    max-width: 400px;
  }

  .timeline-item:nth-child(even) .timeline-content {
    text-align: right;
  }

  .timeline-content h3 {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    color: var(--deep-brown);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .timeline-content p {
    color: var(--warm-brown);
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .timeline-details {
    display: flex;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .timeline-item:nth-child(even) .timeline-details {
    justify-content: flex-end;
  }

  .detail-tag {
    background: var(--light-beige);
    color: var(--warm-brown);
    padding: 0.3rem 0.8rem;
    border-radius: 15px;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    border: 1px solid rgba(196, 163, 115, 0.3);
  }

  .preparation-guide {
    padding: 6rem 0;
    background: var(--light-beige);
  }

  .guide-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(350px, 1fr));
    gap: 3rem;
  }

  .guide-section {
    background: white;
    padding: 3rem;
    border-radius: 16px;
    box-shadow: 0 12px 40px rgba(74, 53, 40, 0.08);
    border: 1px solid rgba(196, 163, 115, 0.2);
    text-align: center;
  }

  .guide-icon {
    width: 80px;
    height: 80px;
    margin: 0 auto 2rem;
    background: var(--warm-cream);
    border-radius: 50%;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(74, 53, 40, 0.1);
  }

  .guide-icon svg {
    width: 40px;
    height: 40px;
  }

  .guide-section h3 {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: 1.6rem;
    color: var(--deep-brown);
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .checklist {
    list-style: none;
    text-align: left;
  }

  .checklist li {
    padding: 0.8rem 0;
    padding-left: 2rem;
    position: relative;
    color: var(--warm-brown);
    line-height: 1.5;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--cream-accents);
  }

  .checklist li:last-child {
    border-bottom: none;
  }

  .checklist li::before {
    content: '✓';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    top: 0.8rem;
    color: var(--muted-gold);
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 1.2rem;
  }

  .anxiety-relief {
    padding: 6rem 0;
    background: white;
  }

  .relief-content {
    text-align: center;
    max-width: 1000px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .relief-content h2 {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    color: var(--deep-brown);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .lead {
    font-size: 1.3rem;
    color: var(--warm-brown);
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
    font-weight: 400;
  }

  .relief-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
    gap: 2rem;
    margin-top: 3rem;
  }

  .relief-card {
    background: var(--warm-cream);
    padding: 2.5rem;
    border-radius: 16px;
    box-shadow: 0 8px 30px rgba(74, 53, 40, 0.08);
    border: 1px solid rgba(196, 163, 115, 0.2);
    transition: transform var(--transition-fast);
  }

  .relief-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-8px);
  }

  .relief-card h4 {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: 1.3rem;
    color: var(--deep-brown);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    font-style: italic;
  }

  .relief-card p {
    color: var(--warm-brown);
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .environment-showcase {
    padding: 6rem 0;
    background: var(--light-beige);
  }

  .showcase-content {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 400px;
    gap: 4rem;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .showcase-text h2 {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    color: var(--deep-brown);
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .showcase-text p {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    color: var(--warm-brown);
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .features-list {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1rem;
  }

  .feature-item {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 1rem;
    padding: 1rem;
    background: white;
    border-radius: 8px;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(74, 53, 40, 0.05);
  }

  .feature-icon {
    width: 32px;
    height: 32px;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .feature-icon svg {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
  }

  .feature-item span {
    color: var(--warm-brown);
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  .visual-placeholder {
    width: 100%;
    height: 400px;
    border-radius: 12px;
    overflow: hidden;
    box-shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(74, 53, 40, 0.15);
  }

  .visual-placeholder svg {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
  }

  .cta-section {
    padding: 6rem 0;
    background: var(--deep-brown);
    text-align: center;
  }

  .cta-content h2 {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    color: white;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .cta-content p {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    color: var(--warm-cream);
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    opacity: 0.9;
  }

  .cta-buttons {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 1rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .btn {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    padding: 1rem 2rem;
    border-radius: 8px;
    font-weight: 500;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: all var(--transition-fast);
    font-size: 1.1rem;
  }

  .btn-primary {
    background: var(--muted-gold);
    color: var(--deep-brown);
  }

  .btn-primary:hover {
    background: #b8956a;
    transform: translateY(-2px);
  }

  .btn-secondary {
    background: transparent;
    color: white;
    border: 2px solid white;
  }

  .btn-secondary:hover {
    background: white;
    color: var(--deep-brown);
    transform: translateY(-2px);
  }

  .contact-info {
    margin-top: 2rem;
    padding-top: 2rem;
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
  }

  .contact-info p {
    color: var(--warm-cream);
    opacity: 0.8;
    margin: 0;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .hero-content h1 {
      font-size: 2.8rem;
    }

    .timeline::before {
      left: 30px;
    }

    .timeline-item {
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: flex-start;
      padding-left: 80px;
    }

    .timeline-item:nth-child(even) {
      flex-direction: column;
    }

    .timeline-number {
      position: absolute;
      left: 0;
      width: 50px;
      height: 50px;
      font-size: 1.2rem;
